{
  "id": 86,
  "nameSimple": "At-Tariq",
  "nameArabic": "الطارق",
  "versesCount": 17,
  "revelationPlace": "makkah",
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 5932,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "verseKey": "86:1",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": " وَٱلسَّمَآءِ وَٱلطَّارِقِ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102036,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "By the sky and the knocker",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752645,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以苍穹和启明星盟誓，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5933,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "verseKey": "86:2",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلطَّارِقُ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102046,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And what can make you know what is the knocker?",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752646,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "你怎能知道启明星是什麽？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5934,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "verseKey": "86:3",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "ٱلنَّجْمُ ٱلثَّاقِبُ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102048,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "It is the piercing star<sup foot_note=230381>1</sup>.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752647,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "是那灿烂的明星。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5935,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "verseKey": "86:4",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِن كُلُّ نَفْسٍ لَّمَّا عَلَيْهَا حَافِظٌ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102050,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "There is no soul but that it has over it a protector.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752648,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "每个人，都有一个保护者。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5936,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "verseKey": "86:5",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَلْيَنظُرِ ٱلْإِنسَـٰنُ مِمَّ خُلِقَ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102053,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So let man observe from what he was created.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752649,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "人应当想一想，他自己是用什么造成的？",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5937,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "verseKey": "86:6",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "خُلِقَ مِن مَّآءٍ دَافِقٍ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102057,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "He was created from a fluid, ejected,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752650,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他是被射出的精液造成的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5938,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "verseKey": "86:7",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَخْرُجُ مِنۢ بَيْنِ ٱلصُّلْبِ وَٱلتَّرَآئِبِ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102059,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Emerging from between the backbone and the ribs.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752651,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那精液是从脊柱和肋骨之间发出的。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5939,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "verseKey": "86:8",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّهُۥ عَلَىٰ رَجْعِهِۦ لَقَادِرٌ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102061,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, He [i.e., Allāh], to return him [to life], is Able.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752652,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "安拉确是能使它复原的，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5940,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "verseKey": "86:9",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "يَوْمَ تُبْلَى ٱلسَّرَآئِرُ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102063,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "The Day when secrets will be put on trial,<sup foot_note=230382>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752653,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "那是一切秘密被揭穿之日。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5941,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "verseKey": "86:10",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَمَا لَهُۥ مِن قُوَّةٍ وَلَا نَاصِرٍ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102037,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Then he [i.e., man] will have no power or any helper.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752654,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他绝没有能力，也没有援助者。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5942,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "verseKey": "86:11",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلرَّجْعِ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102038,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "By the sky which sends back<sup foot_note=230383>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752655,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "以含雨的云，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5943,
      "verseNumber": 12,
      "verseKey": "86:12",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَٱلْأَرْضِ ذَاتِ ٱلصَّدْعِ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102039,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And [by] the earth which splits,<sup foot_note=230384>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752656,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "和有缝的地发誓，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5944,
      "verseNumber": 13,
      "verseKey": "86:13",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوْلٌ فَصْلٌ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102040,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, it [i.e., the Qur’ān] is a decisive statement,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752657,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这确是分别真伪的言辞，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5945,
      "verseNumber": 14,
      "verseKey": "86:14",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلْهَزْلِ",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102041,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "And it is not amusement.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752658,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "这不是笑话。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5946,
      "verseNumber": 15,
      "verseKey": "86:15",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "إِنَّهُمْ يَكِيدُونَ كَيْدًا",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102042,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "Indeed, they are planning a plan,",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752659,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "他们必定要用计谋，",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5947,
      "verseNumber": 16,
      "verseKey": "86:16",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "وَأَكِيدُ كَيْدًا",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102043,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "But I am planning a plan.",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752660,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "我也要用计谋。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5948,
      "verseNumber": 17,
      "verseKey": "86:17",
      "hizbNumber": 59,
      "rubElHizbNumber": 236,
      "rukuNumber": 530,
      "manzilNumber": 7,
      "sajdahNumber": null,
      "textUthmani": "فَمَهِّلِ ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ أَمْهِلْهُمْ رُوَيْدًۢا",
      "pageNumber": 591,
      "juzNumber": 30,
      "translations": [
        {
          "id": 102044,
          "resourceId": 20,
          "text": "So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile.<sup foot_note=230385>1</sup>",
          "languageId": 38,
          "languageName": "english"
        },
        {
          "id": 752661,
          "resourceId": 109,
          "text": "所以你当宽限不信道的人们，你当宽限他们一下。",
          "languageId": 185,
          "languageName": "chinese"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}